WEBVTT

00:09.600 --> 00:11.770
Try again, Twi.
You can do it.

00:12.020 --> 00:14.250
Phew!
This spell's a toughie.

00:14.400 --> 00:16.120
But I feel lucky this time.

00:16.270 --> 00:17.896
One, two...

00:17.896 --> 00:18.860
One, two...
- Hi!

00:22.790 --> 00:24.730
Pinkie, why'd you do that?!

00:24.880 --> 00:26.190
'Cause hugs are funeriffic!

00:26.340 --> 00:28.200
Especially when you throw one
around a friend.

00:28.910 --> 00:30.450
Whatcha doin'?

00:30.600 --> 00:32.860
Trying to turn that apple
into an orange!

00:33.010 --> 00:35.130
But you kind of threw her aim off.

00:35.760 --> 00:37.800
Whee!
What a cute orange birdie!

00:37.950 --> 00:39.550
Do me next, Twilight!
Do me! Do me!

00:40.290 --> 00:43.050
Ooh! Rarity, wanna see Twilight
turn me into an orange?

00:43.200 --> 00:45.400
It's gonna be funna-fun-fun!

00:45.550 --> 00:48.670
As fun as creating an
haute-couture ensemble

00:48.820 --> 00:50.150
that I just finished making?

00:50.300 --> 00:52.310
Delightful, no?

00:52.460 --> 00:53.810
This is terrible!

00:53.960 --> 00:56.500
I admit it's perhaps not
my finest work, but I--

00:56.650 --> 01:00.200
You had total, awesome, amazing fun,
and I missed out on it?!

01:01.620 --> 01:02.500
Wait.

01:02.650 --> 01:04.500
What if there's more awesome,
amazing fun with friends

01:04.650 --> 01:05.920
happening somewhere
in Ponyville right now

01:06.070 --> 01:08.300
that I'm missing out on too?!

01:08.790 --> 01:11.900
We weren't gonna turn her
into an orange. I swear!

01:14.400 --> 01:16.000
Hey, Rainbow Dash.
Whatcha doin'?

01:16.140 --> 01:18.890
This punk cloud got so heavy,
it's making fog.

01:19.040 --> 01:21.800
Figure I'll thin this bad boy out
so it floats back up.

01:21.950 --> 01:23.240
Ooh! Fun!

01:25.000 --> 01:26.000
Gotta go!

01:26.450 --> 01:28.750
Thanks, Pinkie?

01:30.250 --> 01:31.400
Hey, Applejack.

01:31.550 --> 01:33.500
That looks like fun.
Can I join you?

01:33.650 --> 01:36.000
Whee!
Next time, I'll pull you.

01:39.550 --> 01:40.660
Fluttershy!

01:40.960 --> 01:41.960
There...

01:41.960 --> 01:43.100
There... you...

01:43.100 --> 01:43.820
There... you... are...

01:44.230 --> 01:45.370
doing...

01:45.370 --> 01:46.530
doing... anything...

01:46.540 --> 01:47.690
doing... anything... fun?

01:48.230 --> 01:49.780
Not especially.

01:49.930 --> 01:52.890
Oh, good.
Fun is hard!

01:58.450 --> 02:03.450
Season 3 | Episode 3
Too Many Pinkie Pies

02:05.290 --> 02:09.080
